companyName: Invesco KBW Premium Yield Equity REIT ETF
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results (before fees and expenses) of the KBW Nasdaq Premium Yield Equity REIT Index (the "underlying index").
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its total assets in the securities of small- and mid-cap equity REITs in the United States that comprise the underlying index. It generally invests in all of the securities comprising the underlying index in proportion to their weightings in the underlying index.
